full_text:
‚ÑπÔ∏èNote that the $LDO incentives are expected to last at least until staking withdrawals are implemented, as publicly stated by the Lido team.

Though it's also worth considering that staking rewards may continue decreasing as staked amounts of $ETH grow.

https://t.co/5hTk6AT4oD

There are a number of reasons for using $steCRV in @MakerDAO:

- You receive staking rewards from @LidoFinance
- You receive trading fees from @CurveFinance
- You receive additional $LDO incentives

Which adds up to ~7% in total rewards without leverage (vs a 3.5% Stability fee).

CRVV1ETHSTETH-A is the first Vault type (ilk) that uses crop-join, a new adapter that enables collecting liquidity rewards given to holders of a certain asset (or in this case collateral).

üí°Any accrued $LDO rewards are collected each time a user interacts with MakerDAO.
